chunkfs (0.8) unstable; urgency=low

  * Build-depend on perl for any arch to support cross building.
  * Adapt writeoverlay.sh to changed losetup options.
  * Use portable format specifiers for big integers.
  * Update to debhelper compatibility level 9.

 -- Florian Zumbiehl <florz@florz.de>  Thu, 13 Jun 2019 12:35:35 +0200

chunkfs (0.7) unstable; urgency=low

  * Check that file descriptors 0 to 2 are open on startup.
  * Change Debian dependency from deprecated fuse-utils to fuse.

 -- Florian Zumbiehl <florz@florz.de>  Wed, 25 Dec 2013 17:43:35 +0100

chunkfs (0.6) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fix potential filedescriptor leak in unchunkfs_read() in case of
    pread() errors.

 -- Florian Zumbiehl <florz@florz.de>  Wed, 17 Mar 2010 21:02:55 +0100

chunkfs (0.5) unstable; urgency=low

  * Mostly style improvements, in particular more useful help output
  * writeoverlay.sh now uses new losetup option -s to avoid race
    condition in device allocation

